item.title: PostgreSQL Database Management and Data Acquisition
item.description: PostgreSQL Database Management and Data Acquisition Description This project involved using PostgreSQL and SQL to manage and analyze a dataset of hospital readmissions. My goal was to efficiently prepare the data for further analysis and visualization in Tableau.
